				 																THE FEST				 																																	(SRFTI, January 9-13)				 																																	lFrom Tel Aviv to Victoria, Ahmedabad to California, the second international student film festival spans campuses on several continents. Watch out for over 100 films, the open house forums and the Subroto Mitra Memorial Lecture by Oscar-winning sound designer Walter Murch (picture above)				 																THE BOOK				 																																	(Rick Reilly)				 																																	lThe celebrated Sports Illustrated writer carries the bag for the great, the near great and reprobates of golf. The all-in-a-days-work account from the fairways stars a mixed bag ranging from Jack Nicklaus to Deepak Chopra to Donald Trump				 																THE MEET				 																																	(Nazrul Manch, Sat amp; Sun)				 																																	lThe conference of values organised by Rotary International (District 3290) will involve 3,000 delegates from various parts of the world. The high point: Dr Verghese Kurien (picture above) being conferred the 4-way test man of the year award by Governor Viren J. Shah on Saturday THE ALBUM				 																																	(Alka Yagnik, Shankar Mahadevan)				 																																	lA collection of love songs penned by Javed Akhtar (picture above) into which composer Raju Singh has breathed soul. Keep a ear out for the opening numbers Chandni Si and Hazaron Chehron
